graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|container orchestration<br/>REQUIRED| K8s[Kubernetes 1.19+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|metrics collection<br/>OPTIONAL| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|TLS certificates<br/>OPTIONAL| CertManager[cert-manager]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling<br/>OPTIONAL| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler]
    KubeRay -.->|job queueing<br/>OPTIONAL| Kueue[Kueue]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS HA storage<br/>OPTIONAL| Redis[External Redis]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|external access<br/>CRD management| OSRoutes[OpenShift Routes]
    KubeRay -->|metrics scraping<br/>ServiceMonitor| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    KubeRay -.->|dashboard auth<br/>OPTIONAL| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]

    %% Kubernetes API interactions
    KubeRay -->|watch/manage| CRDs[Custom Resources<br/>RayCluster, RayJob, RayService]
    KubeRay -->|create/manage| Pods[Pods]
    KubeRay -->|create/manage| Services[Services]
    KubeRay -->|create/manage| Ingresses[Ingresses]
    KubeRay -->|create/manage| Jobs[Batch Jobs]
    KubeRay -->|create/manage| RBAC[Roles/RoleBindings]

    %% Ray Runtime interactions
    KubeRay -->|pull images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]

    %% User-facing components
    RayHead[Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS, Dashboard, Client]
    RayWorkers[Ray Worker Pods<br/>Distributed Compute]
    RayAutoscaler[Ray Autoscaler<br/>Sidecar]

    KubeRay -->|provisions| RayHead
    KubeRay -->|provisions| RayWorkers
    KubeRay -->|provisions| RayAutoscaler

    RayHead -->|coordinates| RayWorkers
    RayAutoscaler -->|scales| RayWorkers
    RayAutoscaler -->|via K8s API| K8s

    RayHead -.->|HA persistence| Redis

    %% External services accessed by Ray applications (user workloads)
    RayWorkers -.->|model storage<br/>USER WORKLOADS| S3[S3/GCS/Azure Blob<br/>Object Storage]
    RayWorkers -.->|package install<br/>USER WORKLOADS| PyPI[PyPI/Conda Mirrors]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI integration<br/>POTENTIAL| KubeRay
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models<br/>POTENTIAL| KubeRay
    Notebooks[RHOAI Notebooks] -.->|Ray client access<br/>POTENTIAL| RayHead

